<p>With a staff of more than 75 professionals, the Office of Counsel to the Inspector General (OCIG) provides all legal services for OIG. The office is divided into three branches: Administrative and Civil Remedies, Advice, and Industry Guidance.</p>

<p>Learn more about <a href="./ocig.asp">openings with OCIG</a> >></p>

